headline: Bristol-Myers Squibb: Not As Cheap As It Might Seem
summary: At first glance, Bristol-Myers Squibb stock appears cheap with a strong dividend yield. But GAAP earnings are consistently much lower than non-GAAP, which may limit cash for dividends.

headline: Cytokinetics Gains on Positive Late-Stage Cardiomyopathy Study Results
summary: CYTK shares soar 40% after phase III MAPLE-HCM results showed that aficamten outperformed metoprolol in obstructive HCM.
